player instance which contains:
    pin ammo
    cash
    exp
    everything else player related

would make it easier to start a new game and to save/load a game.

on new game:
    currentPlayer = new Player()

on save game:
    write Player values to cookie or whatever

on load game:
    loadedPlayer = new Player();
    load Player values from cookie into loadedPlayer
    currentPlayer = loadedPlayer
